DESCRIPTION:Soviet Union\, 1937. In a prison cell\, thousands of letters f
 rom wrongly accused prisoners\, seeking legal assistance\, are burned. Ag
 ainst all odds\, one of these letters reaches its destination: the office
  of Alexander Kornyev\, a young\, newly appointed local prosecutor.
DTEND:20260510T204500
DTSTAMP:20260504T075030Z
